  <brief_title>Vancomycin Dosage Adjustment for MRSA Infections</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparative Efficacy Study of Vancomycin Dosage Adjustment by Equation-based Method and Vancomycin Trough Concentration Method for Treatment of Infections Caused by Methicillin Resistant Staphylococcus Aureus</official_title>
  <sponsors>
