  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An open-label randomized controlled trial to compare two vancomycin dosage adjustment methods
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      An open-label randomized controlled trial to compare two vancomycin dosage adjustment
      methods; a vancomycin trough concentration method and a equation-based method.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
